rComments: He is really nice and approachable.

Korman is not the most enthusiastic prof but how exciting can you make calculus anyway? Its not an easy course but honestly if you go to all the lectures, take good notes and do LOTS of the practice questions you should be fine!
He might sound sleepy in the first few week of lecture, but as the course goes on-means if you actually study, write down his notes carefully and listen well in class, he is beyond awesome.
